      <title>意大利联合信贷银行出人意料地以 110 亿美元全股票收购 Banco BPM</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-unicredit-offers-buy-banco-bpm-1057-bln-2024-11-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[意大利联合信贷银行（UniCredit）出人意料地以全股票形式收购规模较小的国内同行 Banco BPM，而在此之前，该银行还在寻求收购德国商业银行（Commerzbank），这笔交易存在争议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/italys-unicredit-offers-buy-banco-bpm-1057-bln-2024-11-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Nov 2024 05:25:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
